"The good news is that dogs are fine," Whitmore said.
"They're in good shape."
"They're back with their rightful owners."
Whitmore didn't want to indicate exactly where the dogs were found, in which neighborhood, or the circumstances of the discovery.
"An investigation is under way."
"We don't want to say anything," Whitmore said.
"We're following some leads."
